{"tid":469840,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"其實一個國家啲人嘅性格偏向會唔會取決於佢地嘅語言？","createTime":"2017-11-15T17:29:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T16:37:04.000Z","uid":50610,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6ca3b3fdfc8b8069ebe24abe307d71d07ca72647","tid":469840,"uid":50610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T17:29:49.000Z","msg":"睇到個post話日本人其實好負面/雙面人格<br />\n會唔會關佢地語言事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日文句句都好禮貌客氣，就算鬧都係用字好輕，令到日本人真係想爆人𠴱陣又表達唔到，谷下谷到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n相反睇香港鬧爆人時，可以話到連人地祖宗搬埋出山墳，十分舒壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00eff3da1e9ab38ce2d879784a4b4348176cc425","tid":469840,"uid":156592,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T17:39:31.000Z","msg":"同意，D人成日話香港人無禮貌，唔友善，可能都係因為廣東話好少客氣嘅說話，又無類似敬語嘅野，所以我地表達唔到"},{"pid":"4cc4324e415b68c80db176a72ead8e14053c551e","tid":469840,"uid":27198,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T17:45:50.000Z","msg":"會唔會係文化影響語言多d? <br />\n例如德文好嚴謹係因為德國文化嚴謹？"},{"pid":"9e29346b7905aae393fd060ff7161cb2294cbaa7","tid":469840,"uid":50610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T01:11:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會係文化影響語言多d? <br />\n例如德文好嚴謹係因為德國文化嚴謹？</blockquote><br />\n你意思係文化影響人嘅性格<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果係嘅，我唔否認<br />\n但我意思想話用口表達得到愈多，個人性格扭曲情況相對會比較低，所語言限制左某啲人嘅表達，令到佢地性格扭曲"},{"pid":"d8fcc720090f1ef6d98b8b27f0bf0f789cc64db7","tid":469840,"uid":157734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T01:18:55.000Z","msg":"同意，相反佢地民族既性格會令到佢地側向講咩語言。俄羅斯啲戰鬥民族講句你好都好似想殺哂你全家咁。不過同時間北方種族就係咁既性格，如果唔係成吉思汗點會打到去歐洲。"},{"pid":"9ff9fd2568ba2e0971c673f4722cc2ff10904beb","tid":469840,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T07:36:47.000Z","msg":"大阪人vs東京人<br />\n支那大陸人vs台灣人<br />\n語言只係載具"},{"pid":"c1f21c9b4360d21be99d205b15bc6f0a534e679d","tid":469840,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T07:55:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同意，D人成日話香港人無禮貌，唔友善，可能都係因為廣東話好少客氣嘅說話，又無類似敬語嘅野，所以我地表達唔到</blockquote><br />\n完全唔關事<br />\n廣東話以直古漢語不嬲都好多敬語<br />\n只係你唔識唔用<br />\n好似依家啲人用蝗語用打造、優化一樣<br />\n劣幣驅逐良幣"},{"pid":"f6234570661ac76758e3b11fb3e722a2afdce782","tid":469840,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T07:55:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同意，D人成日話香港人無禮貌，唔友善，可能都係因為廣東話好少客氣嘅說話，又無類似敬語嘅野，所以我地表達唔到</blockquote><br />\n完全唔關事<br />\n廣東話以至<span style=\"color: red;\">至</span>古漢語不嬲都好多敬語<br />\n只係你唔識唔用<br />\n好似依家啲人用蝗語用打造、優化一樣<br />\n劣幣驅逐良幣</blockquote>"},{"pid":"36eb84a76776ba9a98926b57be8f7119bd470e22","tid":469840,"uid":41245,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T07:59:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/16/155929_121c0f31ae9d3308269dfec1d2e67bcc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2F155929_121c0f31ae9d3308269dfec1d2e67bcc.jpg&h=7ab7d13d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e3f64751af47e0d7fe6817bddc0b753d7f37d933","tid":469840,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T08:01:01.000Z","msg":"潛意識上到底有無影響<br />\n<br />\n要高手出招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54809a804691d221f60bdcaf7b50941a5bff904d","tid":469840,"uid":119605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T08:10:14.000Z","msg":"中文敬語<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"403cac8cac04ba3a46a489fedeb204e02c1463d1","tid":469840,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T16:36:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大阪人vs東京人<br />\n支那大陸人vs台灣人<br />\n語言只係載具</blockquote><br />\n講清楚啲好崰<br />\n語言係<span style=\"color: red;\">文化</span>嘅載具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a651bfb651a1b55a8545ab897dfdec026b99a8a4","tid":469840,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T16:37:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/16/155929_121c0f31ae9d3308269dfec1d2e67bcc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2F155929_121c0f31ae9d3308269dfec1d2e67bcc.jpg&h=7ab7d13d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢啲都唔係廣東話嚟嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}